            <!-- <ul conref="bptext-sitelogs.dita#tsk-bptext-sitelogs/ul-duplicate-logged-event-type"><li/></ul> -->
            <ul id="ul-duplicate-logged-event-type">
                <li>If the <uicontrol>Log Type</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>Website</uicontrol> combination doesn't exist, the entry is created.</li>
                <li>If an existing entry has the same <uicontrol>Log Type</uicontrol> and the same <uicontrol>Website</uicontrol>, the existing entry is updated with the new settings.</li>
                <li>If an existing entry has the same <uicontrol>Log Type</uicontrol> but a different <uicontrol>Website</uicontrol>, the entry is created.</li>
            </ul>


            <!-- <p conref="bptext-sitelogs.dita#tsk-bptext-sitelogs/p-notification-settings"></p> -->
            <p id="p-notification-settings">An email is sent to the <uicontrol>Mail To Address</uicontrol> whenever the event exceeds the <uicontrol>Occurrence Threshold</uicontrol>. The timespan is reset after the email is set; e.g., if the threshold is set to <uicontrol>1 Occurrence</uicontrol> in <uicontrol>1 Hour</uicontrol>, the next hour starts when the email is sent.</p>
            <!-- CHRISP : Is the second sentence correct? -->


