            <!-- <note conref="bptext-sitelogs.dita#tsk-bptext-sitelogs/note-host-admin-filtering"></note> -->
            <note type="note" id="note-host-admin-filtering">Hosts/Superusers can filter by site and by event type. Administrators can view only their own site's log and can filter by event type only.</note>

